  "explanation": "Corrected 25 instances of severe character encoding artifacts (mojibake) to their proper German umlauts (ä, ö, ü) and ß. Fixed 5 OCR/typographical errors: 'Textb' to 'Text', 'Aut' to 'Art', 'Íùõc.' to 'etc.', 'Mttte' to 'Mitte', 'R...berg' to 'Nürnberg', and 'Berichthau...' to 'Berichtshaus'. Fixed 1 malformed XML tag by changing <PRIZE> to <PRICE> to ensure well-formed markup. Historical orthography (e.g., 'Praenumeration', 'Liecht', 'Feyertagen', 'gantzen') was intentionally preserved."
